OL,3,CFamily call for inquiry over son's
OL,4,Cdeath in prison
OL,6,FThe family of a 22-year-old prisoner
OL,7,Fwith ADHD who died by suicide inside
OL,8,FMaghaberry Prison in 2018 say they
OL,9,Fwant to see a full, public inquiry
OL,10,Finto Northern Ireland's Prison Service.
OL,12,FDaniel McConville was a remand
OL,13,Fprisoner charged with burglary who had
OL,14,Fbeen inside for 70 days when he was
OL,15,Ffound dead in his cell.
OL,17,FThe father-of-two had struggled with
OL,18,Fdrug issues, and had 80 previous
OL,19,Fconvictions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
