OL,3,CFamily call for inquiry over son's
OL,4,Cdeath in prison
OL,6,FThe jury at an inquest into his death
OL,7,Ffound last month that he took his own
OL,8,Flife, but jurors could not agree
OL,9,Fwhether he intended to do so.
OL,11,FThey found that bullying from jail
OL,12,Fstaff and a lack of appropriate care
OL,13,Fwere factors contributing to Daniel's
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FPaul McConville, Daniel's father, has
OL,17,Fbeen alleging that bullying played a
OL,18,Frole ever since the death, and had
OL,19,Fprotested with placards outside the
OL,20,Fprison for ten months in the wake of
OL,21,Fhis loss.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
