OL,3,CFamily call for inquiry over son's
OL,4,Cdeath in prison
OL,6,F"The truth came out but I knew the
OL,7,Ftruth the whole time," said Paul, who
OL,8,Fsays that family members of other
OL,9,Finmates had shared information about
OL,10,Fevents with him.
OL,12,F"More needs to be done in that prison
OL,13,Fto stop this happening again."
OL,15,FMr McConville said that the new prison
OL,16,Fblock at Maghaberry, which cost
OL,17,F#54million, is a lovely bright
OL,18,Fbuilding, but that a "change of
OL,19,Fattitude" towards prisoners is needed
OL,20,Fto see change.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
