OL,3,CFamily call for inquiry over son's
OL,4,Cdeath in prison
OL,6,FHe acknowledged that there are often
OL,7,Fvictims of crimes committed by
OL,8,Fconvicted prisoners, but said that the
OL,9,Fremoval of freedom is punishment
OL,10,Fenough without bullying inside as well.
OL,12,FThe incident had previously been
OL,13,Fexamined by the Prisoner Ombudsman in
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FThis report resulted in five
OL,17,Frecommendations being made to the
OL,18,FPrison Service and the South Eastern
OL,19,FTrust, which provides Healthcare in
OL,20,Fprisons in NI.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
