OL,3,CFamily call for inquiry over son's
OL,4,Cdeath in prison
OL,6,FHowever now, the family is calling for
OL,7,Fan full inquiry into NI's Prisons.
OL,9,FTheir solicitor, Owen Beattie, says he
OL,10,Fintends to write to the Executive
OL,11,FOffice to make the request.
OL,13,F"There needs to be a full root and
OL,14,Fbranch examination of the conditions
OL,15,Ffaced by prisoners not just in
OL,16,FMaghaberry but in prisons throughout
OL,17,Fthe jurisdiction, and the only
OL,18,Fappropriate format, we say, for that,
OL,19,Fis through a public inquiry," he
OL,20,Frevealed in an interview with UTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
