OL,6,F"We do intend to write to the
OL,7,FExecutive Office, and the other state
OL,8,Factors that are very much important to
OL,9,Fthis process, to call on them to bring
OL,10,Fforward a public inquiry, so that the
OL,11,Fdeath of Daniel McConville and others
OL,12,Fin similar circumstances, can be
OL,13,Fprevented in the future."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
