OL,3,CFamily call for inquiry over son's
OL,4,Cdeath in prison
OL,6,FAsked if he felt there would be pubic
OL,7,Fappetite for such an investigation, Mr
OL,8,FBeattie said: "I think that we as
OL,9,Fcitizens, and the wider state at
OL,10,Flarge, need to be mindful that the
OL,11,Fstate, which is funded through
OL,12,Ftaxpayers money, is responsible for
OL,13,Fthe care of its' fellow citizens in
OL,14,Fthe prison regime, so it's important
OL,15,Fthat steps are taken to ensure that
OL,16,Fthey are properly looked after.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
