OL,6,F"If the question is, will there be a
OL,7,Fwider buy-in, in our view, yes there
OL,8,Fis, because one never knows when a
OL,9,Ffamily member could find themselves in
OL,10,Fthis unfortunate and terrible
OL,11,Fsituation."
OL,13,FBoth the Prison Service and the South
OL,14,FEastern Trust extended their
OL,15,Fsympathies to the McConville family,
OL,16,Fand said that there have been lessons
OL,17,Flearned.
