OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Following a review of the Supporting
OL,8,FPrisoners at Risk procedures, a new
OL,9,Fperson-centred approach is now being
OL,10,Fdelivered which aims to support
OL,11,Fsomeone through a period of crisis or
OL,12,Fdistress, as well as addressing the
OL,13,Froot cause of the issue."
OL,15,FThe South Eastern Trust also
OL,16,Freferenced new practices in a
OL,17,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
