OL,6,F"Every patient who enters prison is
OL,7,Fnow offered a face to face mental
OL,8,Fhealth screening assessment from a
OL,9,FMental Health professional," said a
OL,10,Fstatement.
OL,12,F"We are very committed to learning and
OL,13,Fto improving the health services
OL,14,Favailable for all those in our care."
